		<div class="overflow-hidden content-section">
			<h2>Login</h2>
			<pre><code>
#Request Example
POST {{ apiUrl }}login
{
    "UserEmail": "jse@project.com"
    "UserPassword": "password"
}
        
Result Example:
[
    "result": {
        "UserID": 2,
        "UserFirstName": "Lorem",
        "UserLastName": "İpsum",
        "UserEmail": "jseproject.com",
        "UserTypeName": "Root"
    },
    "token":"SECRET-TOKEN"
]</code></pre>
			<p>For the user login, you need to make a POST call to the URL below :
				<br>
				<code class="higlighted">{{ apiUrl }}login</code>
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="overflow-hidden content-section">
			<h2>My Account Delete</h2>
			<pre><code>
#Request Example
DELETE {{ apiUrl }}my-account
{
    "UserID" : 1
}
        
Reusult Example:
Deletion succeeded.</code></pre>
